      "author": "mntno",
      "description": "### Fixed \r\n\r\nIssues in popups (such as page previews), kanban cards, etc.\r\n\r\n**Limitation**: When editing inside a page preview/popover, the cache cannot be modified.\r\n  - Already cached images are loaded, but a placeholder image is shown for all non-cached images.\r\n  - If images are removed, they will not be deleted from the cache until the note is opened in the normal editor.\r\n\r\n### Changed\r\n\r\n- [New](https://lucide.dev/icons/image-down) download indicator icon.",
